#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode.rst:8
msgid "Barcode"
msgstr "條碼"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode.rst:10
msgid ""
"**Odoo Barcode** allows users to assign barcodes to individual products and "
"product packagings, and track inventory movements using those barcodes. By "
"connecting a barcode scanner, certain inventory processes can be triggered "
"by scanning barcodes."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo 條碼**\\ 允許使用者為個別產品和產品包裝指派條碼，並使用這些條碼追蹤庫"
"存移動。透過連線條碼掃描器，可以透過掃描條碼觸發某些庫存流程。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode.rst:15
msgid "`Odoo Tutorials: Barcode <https://www.odoo.com/slides/barcode-30>`_"
msgstr "\\ `Odoo 教學：條碼\\ <https://www.odoo.com/slides/barcode-30>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations.rst:5
msgid "Daily operations"
msgstr "日常作業"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:3
msgid "Adjust inventory with barcodes"
msgstr "使用條碼調整庫存"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:5
msgid ""
"An *inventory adjustment*, or inventory audit, is the process of verifying "
"the physical stock of products against the quantities recorded in the "
"database. Regular audits ensure accurate inventory records, prevent stock "
"discrepancies, and maintain efficient operations. In a warehouse setting, "
"managers typically assign inventory counts to employees, who then walk to "
"designated locations, scan product barcodes, and adjust quantities as needed."
msgstr ""
"*庫存調整*或庫存盤點，是將產品的實際庫存與資料庫中記錄的數量進行驗證的過程。"
"定期盤點可確保庫存記錄的準確性、防止庫存差異並維持高效率的作業。在倉庫環境中"
"，管理人員通常會將庫存盤點工作分配給員工，員工再前往指定地點掃描產品條碼並視"
"需要調整數量。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:11
msgid ""
"Inventory adjustments can be completed through the **Barcode** application "
"using a compatible scanner, or the Odoo mobile app."
msgstr ""
"庫存調整可以透過\\ **條碼**\\ 應用程式使用相容的掃描器，或使用 Odoo 行動應用"
"程式完成。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:15
msgid ""
"For a list of Odoo-compatible barcode mobile scanners, and other hardware "
"for the **Inventory** and **Barcode** apps, refer to the `Odoo Inventory • "
"Hardware page <https://www.odoo.com/app/inventory-hardware>`_."
msgstr ""
"如需 Odoo 相容的條碼行動掃描器清單，以及\\ **庫存**\\ 和\\ **條碼**\\ 應用程"
"式的其他硬體，請參閱\\ `Odoo 庫存 • 硬體頁面\\ <https://www.odoo.com/app/"
"inventory-hardware>`_。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:20
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/advanced_configuration/sub_assemblies.rst:143
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/count_products`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:23
msgid ""
"Odoo's **Barcode** application provides demo data with barcodes to explore "
"the features of the app. These can be used for testing purposes, and can be "
"printed from the home screen of the app."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 的\\ **條碼**\\ 應用程式提供帶有條碼的示範資料，以便探索應用程式的功能。"
"這些資料可用於測試目的，並可從應用程式的主畫面列印。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:26
msgid ""
"To access this demo data, navigate to the :menuselection:`Barcode app` and "
"click :guilabel:`demo data sheet` or :guilabel:`barcodes` in the banner "
"above the scanner."
msgstr ""
"若要存取此示範資料，請導覽至\\ :menuselection:`條碼應用程式`，然後按一下掃描"
"器上方橫幅中的\\ :guilabel:`示範資料表`或\\ :guilabel:`條碼`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:0
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/transfers_scratch.rst:0
msgid "Demo data prompt pop-up on Barcode app main screen."
msgstr "條碼應用程式主畫面上的示範資料提示彈出視窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:33
msgid "Assigning inventory counts"
msgstr "分配庫存盤點"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:35
msgid ""
"Before performing an inventory count, managers can :ref:`assign <inventory/"
"plan-counts>` counting tasks to employees. This can be done "
"through :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Operations --> Physical Inventory` "
"by selecting specific locations and products for counting, and assigning "
"a :guilabel:`User` to them. Once assigned, users will see pending counts "
"when they open the **Barcode** app."
msgstr ""
"在執行庫存盤點前，管理人員可以透過\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 作"
"業 --> 實地盤點`\\ :ref:`分配 <inventory/plan-counts>`盤點任務給員工。這可透"
"過選擇特定位置和產品進行盤點，並為其分配\\ :guilabel:`使用者`\\ 來完成。分配"
"完成後，使用者打開\\ **條碼**\\ 應用程式時即可看到待處理的盤點。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:41
msgid ""
"To view a requested inventory count, navigate to the :menuselection:`Barcode "
"app` dashboard. If a count has been requested, the number of products to be "
"counted is listed on the :guilabel:`Count Inventory` button."
msgstr ""
"若要檢視請求的庫存盤點，請導覽至\\ :menuselection:`條碼應用程式`\\ Dashboard"
"。如果已請求盤點，要盤點的產品數量會列在\\ :guilabel:`盤點庫存`\\ 按鈕上。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:None
msgid "The Barcode dashboard with an assigned count."
msgstr "具有已分配盤點的條碼 Dashboard。"

