#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:3
msgid "Least packages removal"
msgstr "最少包裝移除"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Least Packages* removal strategy fulfills an order by opening the "
"fewest number of packages, which is ideal for maintaining organized stock "
"without needing to open multiple boxes."
msgstr ""
"*最少包裝*移除策略透過開啟最少數量的包裝來完成訂單，非常適合維持有組織的庫存"
"而無需開啟多個箱子。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:12
msgid ""
"To understand how the removal strategy works, consider the following "
"example, featuring a warehouse that stores packages of flour in bulk "
"packages of `100 kg`."
msgstr ""
"要了解移除策略的運作方式，請考慮以下範例，其特徵是一個倉庫以\\ `100 kg`\\ 的"
"散裝包裝儲存麵粉包裝。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:15
msgid ""
"To minimize moisture and prevent possible loss of product due to spillage "
"and repacking, the least packages removal strategy is used to fill the order "
"by opening the fewest packages of flour, instead of opening multiple "
"packages."
msgstr ""
"為了減少濕氣並防止因溢出和重新包裝而可能導致的產品損失，最少包裝移除策略用於"
"透過開啟最少的麵粉包裝來完成訂單，而不是開啟多個包裝。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:19
msgid ""
"A package of `100 kg` of flour is depleted to `54 kg` after fulfilling some "
"orders. There are other packages of `100 kg` in stock."
msgstr ""
"一包\\ `100 kg`\\ 的麵粉在完成一些訂單後耗盡至\\ `54 kg`。庫存中還有其他\\ "
"`100 kg`\\ 的包裝。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:22
msgid ""
"When an order for `14 kg` of flour is placed, the package of `54 kg` is "
"selected, leaving `40 kg` of flour in the bag. Another order for `80 kg` of "
"flour is placed. An unopened `100 kg` package is used to fulfill the order."
msgstr ""
"當下了一份 `14 kg` 麵粉的訂單時，會選擇 `54 kg` 的包裝，袋中剩餘 `40 kg` 麵粉"
"。又下了另一份 `80 kg` 麵粉的訂單。使用未開封的 `100 kg` 包裝來完成訂單。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:26
msgid ""
"While this temporarily results in two open packages, one for `40 kg` and "
"another for `20 kg`, these open packages are prioritized in the next "
"pickings that are those sizes or smaller."
msgstr ""
"雖然這暫時會導致兩個開啟的包裝，一個為 `40 kg`，另一個為 `20 kg`，但這些開啟"
"的包裝在下次揀貨時會優先用於相同大小或更小的訂單。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:30
msgid "Enabling the least packages removal strategy"
msgstr "啟用最少包裝移除策略"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:35
msgid ""
"The packages feature is used to group products together and is required for "
"the *least packages* removal strategy."
msgstr "包裝功能用於將產品分組在一起，並且是*最少包裝*移除策略所必需的。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:38
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings` "
"and in the :guilabel:`Operations` section, select the check box for "
"the :guilabel:`Packages` feature."
msgstr ""
"導覽至\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 配置 --> 設定`，並在\\ "
":guilabel:`營運`\\ 區段中，選取\\ :guilabel:`包裝`\\ 功能的核取方塊。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:42
msgid "Store products in packages"
msgstr "將產品存放在包裝中"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:44
msgid ""
"First, products are received either in packages or individually. Next, the "
"received products are stored in packages created :ref:`during a transfer "
"<inventory/warehouses_storage/pack>`."
msgstr ""
"首先，產品可以以包裝或單獨的方式接收。接下來，接收的產品會存放在\\ :ref:`轉移"
"期間建立 <inventory/warehouses_storage/pack>`\\ 的包裝中。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:50
msgid ""
"After you have configured your product inventory, set the removal strategy "
"on the :ref:`storage location <inventory/warehouses_storage/lp-location>` "
"or :ref:`product category <inventory/warehouses_storage/lp-category>`."
msgstr ""
"配置產品庫存後，在\\ :ref:`儲存位置 <inventory/warehouses_storage/lp-"
"location>`\\ 或\\ :ref:`產品類別 <inventory/warehouses_storage/lp-category>"
"`\\ 上設定移除策略。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:57
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:58
msgid "On the storage location"
msgstr "在儲存位置上"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:59
msgid ""
"To set a removal strategy on a storage location, you must first enable a "
"couple settings in the **Inventory** configuration settings. "
"Open :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and in "
"the :guilabel:`Warehouse` section, enable :guilabel:`Storage Locations` "
"and :guilabel:`Multi-Step Routes`."
msgstr ""
"若要在儲存位置上設定移除策略，您必須先在 **庫存** 配置設定中啟用幾項設定。開"
"啟\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 配置 --> 設定`，並在\\ :guilabel:`倉"
"庫`\\ 區段中，啟用\\ :guilabel:`儲存位置`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`多步驟路線`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:64
msgid ""
"Next, open :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`. "
"Open an existing location or create a new location. On the location form, "
"under the :guilabel:`Logistics` heading, set the :guilabel:`Removal "
"Strategy`. to :guilabel:`Least Packages`"
msgstr ""
"接下來，開啟\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 配置 --> 位置`。開啟現有位置"
"或建立新位置。在位置表單的\\ :guilabel:`物流`\\ 標題下，將\\ :guilabel:`移除"
"策略`\\ 設定為\\ :guilabel:`最少包裝`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:None
msgid "Set Least Packages as the location's removal strategy."
msgstr "將最少包裝設定為位置的移除策略。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:76
msgid ""
"Configure removal strategies on product categories by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Categories` and "
"selecting the intended product category. Next, in the :guilabel:`Force "
"Removal Strategy` field, select :guilabel:`Least Packages`."
msgstr ""
"透過前往\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 配置 --> 類別`\\ 並選擇預期的產品"
"類別，在產品類別上配置移除策略。接下來，在\\ :guilabel:`強制移除策略`\\ 欄位"
"中，選擇\\ :guilabel:`最少包裝`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:None
msgid "Set Least Packages as the category's removal strategy."
msgstr "將最少包裝設定為類別的移除策略。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:88
msgid ""
"For example, flour is stored in 100-kilogram packages. It is stored in a "
"location with other heavy items. To minimize how far pickers have to walk, "
"the location uses the :doc:`closest location removal strategy "
"<closest_location>`. To further optimize the picking time, and to reduce the "
"number of packages opened during picking, the flour's product category, "
"`Baking Materials`, uses the least packages removal strategy."
msgstr ""
"例如，麵粉以 100 公斤的包裝存放。它與其他重物一起存放在一個位置。為了減少揀貨"
"人員必須行走的距離，該位置使用\\ :doc:`最近位置移除策略 <closest_location>`。"
"為了進一步優化揀貨時間，並減少揀貨期間開啟的包裝數量，麵粉的產品類別「烘焙材"
"料」使用最少包裝移除策略。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:97
msgid ""
"Using the *least packages* removal strategy, the fewest number of packages "
"is used to fulfill an order."
msgstr "使用*最少包裝*移除策略，會使用最少數量的包裝來完成訂單。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:100
msgid ""
"Consider the following example, featuring the product, `Flour (kg)`. The "
"product's :doc:`unit of measure <../../product_management/configure/uom>`, "
"located on the product form, is set to `kg`. The product is stored in "
"packages of `100 kg`, with one remaining package containing `54 kg`. The "
"product category's :guilabel:`Force Removal Strategy` is set "
"to :guilabel:`Least Packages`."
msgstr ""
"請考慮以下範例，產品為\\ `Flour (kg)`\\ 。產品表單上的\\ :doc:`計量單位 <../"
"../product_management/configure/uom>`\\ 設為\\ `kg`\\ 。產品以\\ `100 kg`\\ "
"的包裝儲存，其中一個剩餘包裝包含\\ `54 kg`\\ 。產品類別的\\ :guilabel:`強制移"
"除策略`\\ 設為\\ :guilabel:`最少包裝`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:106
msgid ""
"You can verify the product's on-hand stock in the :guilabel:`Locations` "
"report. Open :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Reporting --> Locations`. "
"Click in the :guilabel:`Search` field to filter by :guilabel:`On Hand`, as "
"well as product."
msgstr ""
"您可以在\\ :guilabel:`庫位`\\ 報告中驗證產品的現有庫存。開啟\\ "
":menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 報告 --> 庫位`\\ 。按一下\\ :guilabel:`搜"
"尋`\\ 欄位，依\\ :guilabel:`現有量`\\ 及產品篩選。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:0
msgid "Show on-hand stock in each package."
msgstr "顯示每個包裝中的現有庫存。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:113
msgid ""
"A sales order is created for eighty kilograms of flour by going to "
"the :menuselection:`Sales app` and creating a new quotation. After "
"clicking :guilabel:`Confirm`, the :ref:`delivery order <inventory/delivery/"
"one-step>` is created."
msgstr ""
"前往\\ :menuselection:`銷售應用程式`\\ 並建立新報價單，以建立八十公斤麵粉的銷"
"售單。按一下\\ :guilabel:`確認`\\ 後，即會建立\\ :ref:`交貨單 <inventory/"
"delivery/one-step>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:117
msgid ""
"On the delivery order, the :guilabel:`Quantity` field displays the amount "
"automatically picked, according to the removal strategy."
msgstr "在送貨單上，\\ :guilabel:`數量`\\ 欄位會根據移除策略顯示自動揀貨的數量。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:120
msgid ""
"For more details about *where* the units were picked, "
"click  :guilabel:`Details` on the product line. Doing so opens "
"the :guilabel:`Detailed Operations` pop-up window, displaying how the "
"reserved items were picked, according to the removal strategy."
msgstr ""
"如需有關揀貨單位*位置*的更多詳細資訊，請按一下產品資料行上的\\ :guilabel:`詳"
"細資訊`\\ 。這樣做會開啟\\ :guilabel:`詳細操作`\\ 彈出視窗，根據移除策略顯示"
"已保留項目的揀貨方式。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:124
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Detailed Operations` pop-up window, the :guilabel:`Pick "
"From` field displays where the quantities to fulfill the :guilabel:`Demand` "
"are picked. Because the order demands eighty kilograms, which exceeds the "
"quantity in the opened package of `54 kg`, an unopened package of `100 kg` "
"is selected."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`詳細操作`\\ 彈出視窗中，:guilabel:`揀貨來源`\\ 欄位顯示從何處"
"揀選數量以滿足\\ :guilabel:`需求`\\ 。由於訂單需要八十公斤，超過已開啟包裝"
"的\\ `54 kg`\\ 數量，因此選擇未開封的\\ `100 kg`\\ 包裝。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:None
msgid "Show which package was picked in the *Pick From* field."
msgstr "在\\ *揀貨來源*\\ 欄位中顯示揀選了哪個包裝。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/least_packages.rst:134
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Least Packages <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/5477/"
"share>`_"
msgstr "`Odoo 教學課程：最少包裝 <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/5477/share>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:3
msgid "LIFO removal"
msgstr "後進先出移除"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Last In, First Out* (LIFO) removal strategy picks the **newest** "
"products on-hand, based on the date they entered a warehouse's stock."
msgstr ""
"*後進先出*（LIFO）移除策略根據產品進入倉庫庫存的日期，揀選現有的\\ **最新**\\"
" 產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:8
msgid ""
"Every time an order is placed for products using the :abbr:`LIFO (Last In, "
"First Out)` strategy, a transfer is created for the lot/serial number that "
"has most recently entered the stock (the **last** lot/serial number that "
"entered the warehouse's inventory)."
msgstr ""
"每次對使用\\ :abbr:`LIFO（後進先出）`\\ 策略的產品下訂單時，系統會為最近進入"
"庫存的批次/序號（進入倉庫庫存的\\ **最後一個**\\ 批次/序號）建立調撥。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:13
msgid ""
"In many countries, the :abbr:`LIFO (Last In, First Out)` removal strategy is "
"banned, since it can potentially result in old, expired, or obsolete "
"products being delivered to customers."
msgstr ""
"在許多國家/地區，\\ :abbr:`LIFO（後進先出）`\\ 移除策略被禁止，因為它可能導致"
"將舊的、過期的或過時的產品交付給客戶。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:19
msgid "Enabling the LIFO removal strategy"
msgstr "啟用 LIFO 移除策略"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:21
msgid ""
"Lots and serial numbers differentiate identical products and track "
"information like arrival or expiration dates. To enable this feature, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Traceability` section, check the box beside :guilabel:`Lots & "
"Serial Numbers` to enable the feature."
msgstr ""
"批次和序號可區分相同的產品並追蹤到貨日期或到期日期等資訊。要啟用此功能，請前"
"往\\ :menuselection:`庫存 --> 配置 --> 設定`\\ 。在\\ :guilabel:`追蹤性`\\ 區"
"段下，勾選\\ :guilabel:`批次與序號`\\ 旁的勾選方格以啟用該功能。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:32
msgid ""
"Next, ensure the intended product is tracked by lots or serial numbers by "
"navigating to the product form in the :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Products --> Products`, then selecting the desired product. On the product "
"form, open the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, select the checkbox next "
"to the :guilabel:`Track Inventory` field, then choose either :guilabel:`By "
"Unique Serial Number` or :guilabel:`By Lots`."
msgstr ""
"接下來，請前往\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 產品 --> 產品`\\ 中的產品表"
"單，確認所需產品已按批次或序號追蹤，然後選擇所需的產品。在產品表單上，開啟\\ "
":guilabel:`一般資訊`\\ 分頁，勾選\\ :guilabel:`追蹤庫存`\\ 欄位旁的勾選方格，"
"然後選擇\\ :guilabel:`按唯一序號`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`按批次`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:51
msgid ""
"After lots or serial numbers have been assigned, set the removal strategy on "
"the product category or storage location."
msgstr "指定批次或序號後，在產品類別或儲存位置上設定移除策略。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:60
msgid ""
"Open :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Locations`. Select "
"the desired location. On the location form, under the :guilabel:`Logistics` "
"heading, select :guilabel:`Last In First Out (LIFO)` from the list of "
"removal strategies."
msgstr ""
"開啟\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 配置 --> 位置`\\ 。選擇所需的位置。在"
"位置表單上，於\\ :guilabel:`物流`\\ 標題下，從移除策略清單中選擇\\ "
":guilabel:`後進先出 (LIFO)`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:None
msgid "Set Last In First Out as the location removal strategy."
msgstr "將後進先出設為位置移除策略。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:70
msgid ""
"Configure removal strategies on product categories by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Categories` and "
"selecting the intended product category. In the :guilabel:`Logistics` "
"section, specify :guilabel:`Last In First Out (LIFO)` in "
"the :guilabel:`Force Removal Strategy` field."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> 配置 --> 類別`\\ 中配置產品類別的移除策"
"略，並選擇所需的產品類別。在\\ :guilabel:`物流`\\ 區段中，於\\ :guilabel:`強"
"制移除策略`\\ 欄位中指定\\ :guilabel:`後進先出 (LIFO)`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:None
msgid "Set Last In First Out as the product category removal strategy."
msgstr "將後進先出設為產品類別移除策略。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:86
msgid ""
"Consider the following example, with the product, `Cinder Block`, which is "
"tracked :guilabel:`By Lots` in the :guilabel:`General Information` tab of "
"the product form. The :guilabel:`Force Removal Strategy` for the cinder "
"block's product category is set to :guilabel:`Last In, First Out (LIFO)`."
msgstr ""
"請考慮以下範例，產品 `Cinder Block` 在產品表單的\\ :guilabel:`一般資訊`\\ 分"
"頁中以\\ :guilabel:`按批次`\\ 追蹤。混凝土磚產品類別的\\ :guilabel:`強制移除"
"策略`\\ 設為\\ :guilabel:`後進先出 (LIFO)`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:90
msgid ""
"The following table lists the cinder blocks in stock and their respective "
"lot numbers."
msgstr "下表列出了庫存中的混凝土磚及其對應的批次號碼。"

