#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Test Environment`/:guilabel:`Production Environment`: Determines "
"whether label creation is for testing and canceled immediately (Test) or "
"generates a real shipping label that is charged to the DHL account "
"(Production)."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`測試環境`\\ ／\\ :guilabel:`正式環境`\\ ：決定標籤建立是用於測"
