#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Debug`/:guilabel:`Debug Requests`: Determines whether API "
"requests and responses are logged in Odoo (turn on :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>` and go to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> "
"Logging`)."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`無除錯`\\ ／\\ :guilabel:`除錯請求`\\ ：決定 API 請求和回應是否"
"記錄在 Odoo 中（開啟\\ :ref:`開發者模式 <developer-mode>`\\ 並前往\\ "
":menuselection:`設定應用程式 --> 技術 --> 記錄`\\ ）。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dispatch.rst:3
msgid "Dispatch management system"
msgstr "出貨管理系統"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dispatch.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *dispatch management system* feature in Odoo is used to plan and build "
"shipments. Key features include:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo 中的\\ *dispatch management system*\\ 功能用於規劃和建立運送。主要功能包"
"括："

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dispatch.rst:8
msgid ""
"**Load building**: Group products for specific carriers, assign "
"those :doc:`batches <../picking_methods/batch>` to loading docks, and manage "
"vehicle assignments based on fleet capacity. This ensures the right products "
"are packed into the appropriate trucks for delivery."
msgstr ""
"**Load building**：為特定承運商分組產品，將這些\\ :doc:`批次 <../"
"picking_methods/batch>`\\ 分配到裝貨碼頭，並根據車隊容量管理車輛分配。這確保"
"將正確的產品裝入適當的卡車進行配送。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dispatch.rst:11
msgid ""
":doc:`Fleet management <../../../../hr/fleet>`: Track and manage the "
"capacity of in-house delivery vehicles."
msgstr "\\ :doc:`車隊管理 <../../../../hr/fleet>`\\ ：追蹤並管理內部配送車輛的容量。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dispatch.rst:17
msgid ""
"To use the dispatch management system, the following setup must be completed:"
msgstr "要使用調度管理系統，必須完成以下設定："

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dispatch.rst:19
msgid ":ref:`Install <general/install>` the **Fleet** application."
msgstr "\\ :ref:`安裝 <general/install>`\\ **車隊**應用程式。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dispatch.rst:20
msgid ""
"Configure vehicle :ref:`capacity (volume and weight) <inventory/"
