msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`New` to add a new category, or click into an existing "
"category to modify it. In the :guilabel:`Name` field, enter the type of "
"vehicle (e.g., `Pick-up truck`, `Van`, or `Cargo truck`). Then, enter the "
"vehicle capacity in the :guilabel:`Max Weight` (in kilograms) "
"and :guilabel:`Max Volume` (in cubic meters) fields."
msgstr ""
"接著，按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 以加入新類別，或按一下現有類別以進行修改。"
"在\\ :guilabel:`名稱`\\ 欄位中，輸入車輛類型（例如 `皮卡車`、`箱型車`或 `貨"
"車`）。然後，在\\ :guilabel:`最大重量`\\ （以公斤為單位）和\\ :guilabel:`最大"
"體積`\\ （以立方公尺為單位）欄位中輸入車輛容量。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dispatch.rst:None
