#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:118
msgid ""
"Configure a Starshipit delivery method in Odoo by filling out the fields on "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` form as follows:"
msgstr ""
"在 Odoo 中配置 Starshipit 貨運方法，請如下填寫\\ :guilabel:`貨運方法`\\ 表單"
