#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:7
msgid ""
"Integrating a USPS account with Odoo's **Inventory** app makes it possible "
"to calculate delivery rates and generate delivery labels within Odoo. This "
"is accomplished by enabling the USPS shipping connector, then configuring at "
"least one delivery method."
msgstr ""
"將 USPS 帳戶與 Odoo 的\\ **庫存**\\ 應用程式整合，可以在 Odoo 中計算運送費率"
"並產生運送標籤。這是透過啟用 USPS 運送連接器，然後配置至少一種運送方式來完成"
"的。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:14
msgid ""
"To enable the USPS shipping connector, open the :menuselection:`Apps` app "
"from the main Odoo dashboard. In the :guilabel:`Search` field, search for "
"`USPS`  and click :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr ""
"若要啟用 USPS 運送連接器，請從 Odoo 主 Dashboard 開啟\\ :menuselection:`應用"
"程式`\\ 應用程式。在\\ :guilabel:`搜尋`\\ 欄位中搜尋 `USPS`，然後按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`安裝`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:17
msgid ""
"After the shipping connector is installed, the USPS connector is enabled by "
"default."
msgstr "安裝運送連接器後，USPS 連接器預設為啟用。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/usps.rst:20
msgid "Configure USPS business account"
msgstr "配置 USPS 商業帳戶"

