#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:275
msgid ""
"No effect on the |RFQ|/|PO|; adds buffer days in the :ref:`JIT forecast "
"window <inventory/warehouses_storage/forecasted-date>`."
msgstr ""
"對\\ |RFQ|/|PO|\\ 沒有影響；在\\ :ref:`JIT 預測視窗 <inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/forecasted-date>`\\ 中加入緩衝天數。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:277
msgid ""
":ref:`Vendor lead time <inventory/warehouses_storage/purchase-vendor-lt>`"
msgstr ":ref:`供應商交貨時間 <inventory/warehouses_storage/purchase-vendor-lt>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:278
msgid ""
"Days from the confirmation of a purchase order (PO) to the receipt of "
"products."
msgstr "從確認採購單（PO）到收到產品的天數。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:279
msgid ""
"Affects the |RFQ|/|PO|, adds buffer days in the :ref:`JIT forecast window "
"<inventory/warehouses_storage/forecasted-date>`."
msgstr ""
"影響\\ |RFQ|/|PO|\\ ，在\\ :ref:`JIT 預測視窗 <inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"forecasted-date>`\\ 中加入緩衝天數。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:None
msgid ""
"Timeline of days to purchase and vendor lead time between the PO deadline "
"and receipt date."
msgstr "採購天數和供應商交貨時間在 PO 截止日期和收貨日期之間的時間軸。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:286
msgid "To tie the purchase dates and lead times together, consider this:"
msgstr "要將採購日期和交貨時間聯繫起來，請考慮以下內容："

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/lead_times.rst:288
