msgstr "此外，Dashboard 還包括以下按鈕："

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`To Send`: orders in the |RFQ| stage that have not been sent to "
"the vendor."
msgstr ":guilabel:`待傳送`：處於\\ |RFQ|\\ 階段且尚未傳送給供應商的訂單。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Waiting`: |RFQs| that have been sent by email, and are waiting on "
"vendor confirmation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`等待中`：已透過電子郵件傳送且正在等待供應商確認的\\ |RFQs|。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Late`: |RFQs| or |POs| where the :guilabel:`Order Deadline` has "
"passed."
msgstr ":guilabel:`逾期`：:guilabel:`訂單截止日期`\\ 已過的\\ |RFQs|\\ 或\\ |POs|。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:None
msgid "RFQ dashboard with orders and order statuses."
msgstr "包含訂單和訂單狀態的報價請求 Dashboard。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:95
msgid ""
"In addition to view options, the :guilabel:`Requests for Quotation` "
"dashboard provides :guilabel:`Filters` and :guilabel:`Group By` options, "
"accessible via the search bar drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"除了檢視選項外，:guilabel:`報價請求` Dashboard 還提供\\ :guilabel:`篩選器`\\ "
"和\\ :guilabel:`分組依據`\\ 選項，可透過搜尋列下拉式選單存取。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:99
msgid ":doc:`../../../essentials/search`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../essentials/search`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:104
msgid "Create a new |RFQ|"
msgstr "建立新的\\ |RFQ|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:106
msgid ""
"To create a new |RFQ|, click the :guilabel:`New` button on the top-left "
"corner of the :guilabel:`Requests for Quotation` dashboard to reveal a new |"
"PO| form."
msgstr ""
"要建立新的\\ |RFQ|，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`報價請求` Dashboard 左上角的\\ "
":guilabel:`新增`\\ 按鈕，以顯示新的\\ |PO|\\ 表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:109
msgid "Start by assigning a :guilabel:`Vendor`."
msgstr "首先指定\\ :guilabel:`供應商`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:111
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Vendor Reference` field points to the sales and delivery "
"order numbers sent by the vendor. This comes in handy once products are "
"received, and the |PO| needs to be matched to the delivery order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`供應商參考`\\ 欄位指向供應商傳送的銷售和交貨訂單編號。當收到產品時"
"，需要將\\ |PO|\\ 與交貨訂單配對，此時這個欄位就派上用場了。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:115
msgid ""
"With the :doc:`Purchase Agreements feature <blanket_orders>` activated, "
"the :guilabel:`Blanket Order` field appears, referring to long-term purchase "
"agreements on recurring orders with set pricing. To view and configure "
"blanket orders, head to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Orders --> Purchase "
"agreements`."
msgstr ""
"啟用\\ :doc:`採購協議功能 <blanket_orders>`\\ 後，:guilabel:`總括訂單`\\ 欄位"
"會出現，用於指定針對定期訂單的長期採購協議及其定價。若要檢視並配置總括訂單，"
"請前往\\ :menuselection:`採購應用程式 --> 訂單 --> 採購協議`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:121
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Purchase agreements` view only appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Blanket Order` setting is enabled. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Configuration --> Settings`, then tick "
"the :guilabel:`Blanket Orders` checkbox."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`採購協議`\\ 檢視僅在啟用\\ :guilabel:`總括訂單`\\ 設定後才會出現。"
"若要啟用，請前往\\ :menuselection:`採購應用程式 --> 配置 --> 設定`\\ ，然後勾"
"選\\ :guilabel:`總括訂單`\\ 勾選方格。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:125
msgid ""
"Next, configure an :guilabel:`Order Deadline`, which is the date by which "
"the vendor must confirm their agreement to supply the products."
msgstr ""
"接下來，配置\\ :guilabel:`訂單截止日期`\\ ，即供應商必須確認同意供應產品的日"
"期。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:129
msgid ""
"After the :guilabel:`Order Deadline` is exceeded, the |RFQ| is marked as "
"late, but the products can still be ordered."
msgstr ""
"當超過\\ :guilabel:`訂單截止日期`\\ 後，|RFQ|\\ 會標記為逾期，但仍可訂購產品"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expected Arrival` is automatically calculated based on "
"the :guilabel:`Order Deadline` and vendor lead time. Tick the checkbox "
"for :guilabel:`Ask confirmation` to ask the vendor to confirm the shipping "
"date by email."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`預計到達`\\ 會根據\\ :guilabel:`訂單截止日期`\\ 及供應商前置時間自"
"動計算。勾選\\ :guilabel:`要求確認`\\ 的勾選方格，以透過電子郵件要求供應商確"
"認出貨日期。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:136
msgid ""
"With the :doc:`Storage Locations feature <../../inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/use_locations>` activated, the :guilabel:`Deliver to` "
"field appears, which specifies which warehouse operation (set in the "
"**Inventory** app) is used to receive the shipment."
msgstr ""
"啟用\\ :doc:`儲存位置功能 <../../inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/use_locations>`\\ 後，:guilabel:`配送至`\\ 欄位會出現，"
"用於指定使用哪個倉庫作業（在\\ **庫存**\\ 應用程式中設定）來接收貨件。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:141
msgid ""
"Select the receiving warehouse address here, or select :guilabel:`Dropship` "
"to indicate that this order is to be shipped directly to the end customer. "
"When :guilabel:`Dropship` is selected, the :guilabel:`Dropship address` "
"field is enabled. Contact names auto-populate here from the **Contacts** app."
msgstr ""
"在此選擇接收倉庫地址，或選擇\\ :guilabel:`直接配送`\\ 以表示此訂單將直接運送"
"給最終客戶。選擇\\ :guilabel:`直接配送`\\ 時，:guilabel:`直接配送地址`\\ 欄位"
"會啟用。聯絡人名稱會從\\ **聯絡人**\\ 應用程式自動填入此處。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:147
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Dropship` options only appear if the :guilabel:`Dropshipping` "
"setting is enabled in the **Inventory** app. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, then tick "
"the :guilabel:`Dropshipping` checkbox."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`直接配送`\\ 選項僅在\\ **庫存**\\ 應用程式中啟用\\ :guilabel:`直接"
"配送`\\ 設定後才會出現。若要啟用，請前往\\ :menuselection:`庫存應用程式 --> "
"配置 --> 設定`\\ ，然後勾選\\ :guilabel:`直接配送`\\ 勾選方格。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:152
msgid ""
"To create |RFQs| using different currencies, each currency needs to be "
"enabled in the **Invoicing** app settings. See :doc:`../../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/prices/currencies` to learn more."
msgstr ""
"若要使用不同貨幣建立\\ |RFQs|\\ ，需要在\\ **發票**\\ 應用程式設定中啟用各個"
"貨幣。請參閱\\ :doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/"
"currencies`\\ 以瞭解更多資訊。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:157
msgid "Products tab"
msgstr "產品分頁"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:159
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Products` tab, add the products to be ordered. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and type in the product name, or select the "
"item from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`產品`\\ 分頁中，加入要訂購的產品。按一下\\ :guilabel:`加入產"
"品`\\ ，然後輸入產品名稱，或從下拉式選單中選擇項目。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:162
msgid ""
"To create a new product and add it, type the new product name in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` column, select :guilabel:`Create [product name]` "
"from the resulting drop-down menu and manually add the unit price. "
"Alternatively, select :guilabel:`Create and edit...` to be taken to the "
"product form for that new item."
msgstr ""
"若要建立新產品並加入，請在\\ :guilabel:`產品`\\ 欄中輸入新產品名稱，從產生的"
"下拉式選單中選擇\\ :guilabel:`建立 [產品名稱]`\\ ，然後手動加入單價。或者，選"
"擇\\ :guilabel:`建立並編輯...`\\ 以前往該新項目的產品表單。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Catalog` can also be selected to navigate to a product menu from "
"the chosen vendor. From here, products can be added to the cart."
msgstr ""
"也可以選擇\\ :guilabel:`目錄`\\ 以從所選供應商瀏覽產品選單。從這裡可以將產品"
"加入購物車。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:171
msgid ""
"To make adjustments to products and prices, access the product form by "
"clicking the :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` icon that "
"becomes available upon hovering over the :guilabel:`Product` name."
msgstr ""
"若要調整產品和價格，請按一下將滑鼠游標懸停在\\ :guilabel:`產品`\\ 名稱上時出"
"現的\\ :icon:`oi-arrow-right`\\ :guilabel:`（右箭頭）`\\ 圖示，以存取產品表單"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:176
msgid "Send the |RFQ|"
msgstr "傳送\\ |RFQ|"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:178
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Send by Email` reveals a :guilabel:`Compose Email` pop-"
"up window, with a :guilabel:`Purchase: Request for Quotation` template "
"loaded, ready to send to the vendor's email address (configured in the "
"**Contacts** app)."
msgstr ""
"按一下\\ :guilabel:`透過電子郵件傳送`\\ 會顯示\\ :guilabel:`撰寫電子郵件`\\ "
"彈出視窗，其中載入了\\ :guilabel:`採購：報價請求`\\ 範本，準備傳送至供應商的"
"電子郵件地址（在\\ **聯絡人**\\ 應用程式中配置）。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:182
msgid ""
"After crafting the desired message, click :guilabel:`Send`. Once sent, the |"
"RFQ| moves to the :guilabel:`RFQ Sent` stage."
msgstr ""
"撰寫所需訊息後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`傳送`\\ 。傳送後，|RFQ|\\ 會移至\\ "
":guilabel:`已傳送報價請求`\\ 階段。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:185
msgid "Clicking :guilabel:`Print RFQ` downloads a PDF of the |RFQ|."
msgstr "按一下\\ :guilabel:`列印報價請求`\\ 會下載\\ |RFQ|\\ 的 PDF。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:188
msgid ":doc:`../../../essentials/contacts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../essentials/contacts`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:193
msgid "Confirm order"
msgstr "確認訂單"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:195
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Confirm Order` directly transforms the |RFQ| into an "
"active |PO|."
msgstr "按一下\\ :guilabel:`確認訂單`\\ 會直接將\\ |RFQ|\\ 轉換為有效的\\ |PO|\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:198
msgid ""
"Odoo tracks communications on each order through the chatter of the |PO| "
"form. This shows the emails sent between the user and the contact, as well "
"as any internal notes and activities. Messages, notes, and activities can "
"also be logged on the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Odoo\\ 透過\\ |PO|\\ 表單的聊天欄追蹤每筆訂單的通訊。這會顯示使用者與聯絡人之"
"間寄送的電子郵件，以及任何內部備註和活動。訊息、備註和活動也可以記錄在聊天欄"
"中。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:202
msgid "Once an |RFQ| is confirmed, it creates a |PO|."
msgstr "|RFQ|\\ 經過確認後，會建立一個\\ |PO|。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:204
msgid ""
"On the new |PO|, the :guilabel:`Order Deadline` field changes "
"to :guilabel:`Confirmation Date`, which displays the date and time the user "
"confirmed the order."
msgstr ""
"在新的\\ |PO|\\ 上，:guilabel:`訂單截止日期`\\ 欄位會變更為\\ :guilabel:`確認"
"日期`，顯示使用者確認訂單的日期和時間。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:207
msgid ""
"Depending on the user's chosen configuration in the **Purchase** app "
"settings, a *vendor bill* is created once products have been ordered or "
"received. For more information, refer to the documentation on :doc:`managing "
"vendor bills <manage>`."
msgstr ""
"視使用者在\\ **採購**\\ 應用程式設定中選擇的配置而定，在產品訂購或收到後會建"
"立\\ *供應商帳單*。如需更多資訊，請參閱\\ :doc:`管理供應商帳單 <manage>`\\ 的"
"使用說明。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:212
msgid ""
"After an order is placed, clicking :guilabel:`Receive Products` records the "
"reception of new products into the database."
msgstr "下單後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`接收產品`\\ 會將新產品的接收記錄到資料庫中。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq.rst:216
msgid ""
"With the **Inventory** app installed, confirming a |PO| automatically "
"creates a receipt document, with the product information and expected "
"arrival dates automatically populated."
msgstr ""
"安裝\\ **庫存**\\ 應用程式後，確認\\ |PO|\\ 會自動建立一個收貨文件，並自動填"
"入產品資訊和預計到貨日期。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products.rst:5
msgid "Products"
msgstr "產品"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:40
msgid "Import vendor pricelist"
msgstr "匯入供應商價目表"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:5
msgid ""
"Set vendor prices to auto-populate requests for quotations (RFQs) or "
"purchase orders (POs) with the unit price, once the product is added, which "
"reduces errors and saves time."
msgstr ""
"設定供應商價格，以便在加入產品後，自動填入報價請求（RFQ）或採購訂單（PO）的單"
"價，從而減少錯誤並節省時間。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:8
msgid ""
"In Odoo, vendor pricelists can be :ref:`added individually <purchase/"
"products/pricelist>` on the product form, or :ref:`imported in bulk "
"<purchase/products/import-pricelist>`, via an XLSX or CSV file."
msgstr ""
"在\\ Odoo\\ 中，供應商價目表可以在產品表單上\\ :ref:`單獨加入 <purchase/"
"products/pricelist>`，或透過\\ XLSX\\ 或\\ CSV\\ 檔案\\ :ref:`批次匯入 "
"<purchase/products/import-pricelist>`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:13
msgid ""
"Please review this :doc:`import guide <../../../essentials/"
"export_import_data>` before uploading vendor pricelists."
msgstr ""
"上傳供應商價目表之前，請先檢閱此\\ :doc:`匯入指南 <../../../essentials/"
"export_import_data>`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:19
msgid "On product form"
msgstr "在產品表單上"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:21
msgid ""
"To manually add the vendor price on the product form, go to "
"the :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Products --> Products`, and click the "
"desired product."
msgstr ""
"若要在產品表單上手動加入供應商價格，請前往\\ :menuselection:`採購應用程"
"式 --> 產品 --> 產品`，然後按一下所需的產品。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:25
msgid ""
"Product forms are accessible from multiple apps, such as **Sales**, "
"**Inventory**, and **Manufacturing**."
msgstr "產品表單可從多個應用程式存取，例如\\ **銷售**、**庫存**\\ 和\\ **製造**。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:28
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Purchase` tab of the product form, input the vendor and "
"their price, to have this information auto-populate on a request for "
"quotation each time the product is listed."
msgstr ""
"在產品表單的\\ :guilabel:`採購`\\ 分頁中，輸入供應商及其價格，以便在每次列出"
"產品時，將此資訊自動填入報價請求中。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:32
msgid ""
":ref:`Vendor pricelist on product form <purchase/manage_deals/vendor-"
"pricelist>`"
msgstr ":ref:`產品表單上的供應商價目表 <purchase/manage_deals/vendor-pricelist>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:None
msgid "Vendor pricelist on product form."
msgstr "產品表單上的供應商價目表。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:42
msgid ""
"To import vendor pricelists, ensure the XLSX or CSV file is accurately "
"completed. The best way to obtain a correctly formatted template, including "
"product names, references, and vendor details, is to first :ref:`export a "
"pricelist <purchase/products/export-price>` from the database."
msgstr ""
"若要匯入供應商價目表，請確保\\ XLSX\\ 或\\ CSV\\ 檔案已正確完成。取得格式正確"
"的範本（包括產品名稱、參考編號和供應商詳細資料）的最佳方法是先從資料庫\\ "
":ref:`匯出價目表 <purchase/products/export-price>`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:46
msgid ""
"Modify the exported file, as needed, then import it back into the Odoo "
"database."
msgstr "根據需要修改匯出的檔案，然後將其匯入回\\ Odoo\\ 資料庫。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:51
msgid "Export pricelist"
msgstr "匯出價目表"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:53
msgid ""
"To export a pricelist, go to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> Configuration "
"--> Vendor Pricelists`."
msgstr ""
"若要匯出價目表，請前往\\ :menuselection:`採購應用程式 --> 配置 --> 供應商價目"
"表`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:55
msgid "On the page, tick the checkbox(es) for the desired vendor pricelists."
msgstr "在頁面上，勾選所需供應商價目表的\\ :guilabel:`勾選方格`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:57
msgid ""
"Then, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button that appears, and "
"choose :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Export` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"然後，按一下出現的\\ :icon:`fa-cog`\\ :guilabel:`動作`\\ 按鈕，並從下拉式選單"
"中選擇\\ :icon:`fa-upload`\\ :guilabel:`匯出`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:None
msgid "Show selected exported fields, with the Export button visible."
msgstr "顯示已選取的匯出欄位，可看到「匯出」按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:63
msgid ""
"In the resulting pop-up window, fields listed under the :guilabel:`Fields to "
"export` section are included in the exported file. To add more fields, find "
"the desired field in the :guilabel:`Available fields` section, and click "
"the :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon to the right of the field."
msgstr ""
"在彈出的視窗中，:guilabel:`要匯出的欄位`\\ 區段下列出的欄位會包含在匯出的檔案"
"中。若要加入更多欄位，請在\\ :guilabel:`可用欄位`\\ 區段中找到所需欄位，然後"
"按一下欄位右側的\\ :icon:`fa-plus`\\ :guilabel:`（加號）`\\ 圖示。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:69
msgid ""
"To update to existing records, tick the :guilabel:`I want to update data "
"(import-compatible export)` checkbox, and refer to the section on "
"the :ref:`External ID <purchase/products/external-id>` field."
msgstr ""
"若要更新現有記錄，請勾選\\ :guilabel:`我想要更新資料（相容匯入的匯出）`\\ 勾"
"選方格，並參閱有關\\ :ref:`外部 ID <purchase/products/external-id>`\\ 欄位的"
"章節。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:73
msgid ""
"For details on commonly-used fields for importing vendor pricelists, see "
"the :ref:`Common fields <purchase/products/common-fields>` section."
msgstr ""
"有關匯入供應商價目表常用欄位的詳細資訊，請參閱\\ :ref:`常用欄位 <purchase/"
"products/common-fields>`\\ 章節。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:76
msgid ""
"Select the desired :guilabel:`Export Format`: :guilabel:`XLSX` "
"or :guilabel:`CSV`."
msgstr ""
"選擇所需的\\ :guilabel:`匯出格式`：:guilabel:`XLSX`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`CSV`\\ "
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:78
msgid ""
"To save the selected fields as a template, click the :guilabel:`Template` "
"field, and select :guilabel:`New template` from the drop-down menu. Type the "
"name of the new template, and click the :icon:`fa-floppy-"
"o` :guilabel:`(save)` icon. After that, the template is a selectable option "
"when clicking the :guilabel:`Template` field."
msgstr ""
"若要將選取的欄位儲存為範本，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`範本`\\ 欄位，並從下拉式選"
"單中選擇\\ :guilabel:`新增範本`\\ 。輸入新範本的名稱，然後按一下\\ :icon:`fa-"
"floppy-o`\\ :guilabel:`（儲存）`\\ 圖示。之後，該範本在按一下\\ :guilabel:`範"
"本`\\ 欄位時就會成為可選擇的選項。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:83
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Export`."
msgstr "最後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`匯出`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:86
msgid ""
"With :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` turned on, the column names of "
"the exported file display the *field name* with the *technical name* in "
"parenthesis."
msgstr ""
"開啟\\ :ref:`開發人員模式 <developer-mode>`\\ 後，匯出檔案的欄名會顯示*欄位名"
"稱*，並在括號中顯示*技術名稱*。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:0
msgid "Exporting vendor pricelist."
msgstr "匯出供應商價目表。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:93
msgid ""
"Export vendor pricelist in XLSX format. It includes :guilabel:`Product "
"Template` and other fields in the :guilabel:`Fields to export` section."
msgstr ""
"以 XLSX 格式匯出供應商價目表。包含\\ :guilabel:`產品範本`\\ 以及\\ "
":guilabel:`要匯出的欄位`\\ 區段中的其他欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:99
msgid "External ID"
msgstr "外部識別碼"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:101
msgid ""
"*External ID* is a unique identifier used to update existing vendor "
"pricelists. Without it, imported records create new entries, instead of "
"updating existing ones. Including this field in the XLSX or CSV, indicates "
"the line replaces an existing vendor pricelist in the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"*外部 ID* 是用於更新現有供應商價目表的唯一識別碼。沒有它，匯入的記錄會建立新"
"的記項，而不是更新現有記項。在 XLSX 或 CSV 中包含此欄位，表示該資料行會取代 "
"Odoo 資料庫中的現有供應商價目表。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:0
msgid "Show 'Ready Mat' appear twice."
msgstr "顯示「Ready Mat」出現兩次。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase/products/pricelist.rst:109
msgid ""
"`Ready Mat` appears twice because the external ID was omitted during the "
